that story was corrected to reflect that police now say that Lamb made the emergency call after he shot Schmidt , and that Lamm , in his emergency call , called Prentiss his wife , but there is no indication that the two have ever married .
Toys R Us plans to hire less labor for Christmas
Toys R Us says it won &apos;t hire as many Christmas season employees as last year , but the toy and baby products retailer says it will give the current staff and seasonal workers a chance to work more hours .
the company said it plans to hire 40,000 people in stores and distribution centers across the country , while still hiring 45,000 workers in the Christmas 2014 period .
most jobs will be part @-@ time jobs .
the company said it will begin application talks this month and that staff numbers will rise from October to December .
while the holidays themselves are months away , the Christmas business is moving closer , and companies are preparing to hire temporary workers to equip stores with employees who sell , ship and deliver products .
