members of the New York @-@ based Baruch College Pi @-@ Delta Psi Brotherhood attacked Chun &quot; Michael &quot; Deng during a introductory ritual in September 2013 and delayed his transport to the hospital , which contributed to his death , police said .
officials said he was saddled with connected eyes with a 30 @-@ pound backpack full of sand , and repeatedly attacked while trying to get over a frozen field on a target .
Mr. Deng eventually complained about headaches , then he fell unconscious .
members of the Pi @-@ Delta Psi Brotherhood did not call the emergency number 911 after Deng became powerless and allegedly waited an hour before they brought him to hospital , according to police .
however , they had the time to switch Dengs clothing , to goose his symptoms and Andy Meng , the Brotherhood &apos;s national president , to contact counsel , police chief Chris Wagner said at a news conference .
