the &quot; exception &quot; concerned permission for a special form regarding roof construction .
thus , a &quot; semi @-@ roof with a non @-@ attached first and attic &quot; is to be built .
background to the planning is the planned use of the roof area for solar installations : &quot; this brings us together a wonderfully large south roof , &quot; Mayor Josef Steigenberger said at the meeting .
the &quot; liberation &quot; was , in turn , about the attainment , which should be below 10 degrees for energy reasons , unlike the Bebauplan .
this significantly reduces the volume of the hall .
