hundreds of refugees to fall in Wiesbaden
a train with hundreds of refugees is on its way to Hessen .
his arrival was expected for the night on Wednesday .
the people who travelled there will then be housed in shelters in Wiesbaden , as the city of Wiesbaden reported Tuesday night .
it estimated between 450 and 750 refugees .
several sports halls of the province &apos;s capital had been prepared for this case in recent days .
up to 1000 refugees can be temporarily accommodated there .
they will then be distributed to other municipalities .
over the past ten days alone , 7500 people had arrived in Hessen , according to the government &apos;s Board of Directors responsible for initial recording .
Frankfurt and Hanau have also set up emergency accommodation in Sporthalle because of the large number of refugees .
